    "Html": "\r\n<p>Hy,</p>\r\n<p>I use Irony in this context&nbsp; <a href=\"http://www.sqlservercentral.com/articles/Full-Text&#43;Search&#43;(2008)/64248/\">\r\nA Google-like Full Text Search</a> - an article by Michael Coles about Google-to-SQL Server full-text search query converter based on Irony.</p>\r\n<p>For the latin language, French, english, Spanish, Irony works well but for the arabic language, the compiler causes an error.</p>\r\n<p>The word to search :&nbsp; &quot;مخصصة&quot; for example</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#2b91af; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#2b91af; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#2b91af; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-size:x-small\"></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-size:x-small\"></p>\r\n<p>_compiler =<span style=\"color:#0000ff; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff; font-size:x-small\">new</span></span><span style=\"font-size:x-small\">\r\n</span><span style=\"color:#2b91af; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#2b91af; font-size:x-small\">LanguageCompiler</span></span><span style=\"font-size:x-small\">(_grammar);</span><span style=\"color:#2b91af; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#2b91af; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#2b91af; font-size:x-small\">\r\n</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#2b91af; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#2b91af; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#2b91af; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#2b91af; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#2b91af; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#2b91af; font-size:x-small\"></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>AstNode <span style=\"font-size:x-small\">oot = _compiler.Parse(sFind);<span style=\"font-size:x-small\">\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n</span></span></span>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-size:x-small\">&nbsp;</span></span>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-size:x-small\">&nbsp;</span></span>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</span></span>\r\n<p></p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#2b91af; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#2b91af; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#2b91af; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#2b91af; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-size:x-small\"><font size=\"2\"></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</font></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff; font-size:x-small\">if</span></span><span style=\"font-size:x-small\"> (_compiler.Context.Errors.Count == 0)</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-size:x-small\"></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\nERROR Invalid character: 'م<span style=\"font-size:x-small\"></span>\r\n<p>&nbsp;Thx for your help.</p>\r\n</span></span>\r\n<p></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>_grammar =<span style=\"color:#0000ff; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff; font-size:x-small\">new</span></span><span style=\"font-size:x-small\">\r\n</span><span style=\"color:#2b91af; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#2b91af; font-size:x-small\">SearchGrammar</span></span><span style=\"font-size:x-small\">();</span><span style=\"font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-size:x-small\">\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n",
